channel.title: Connection problems with people joining my server?
channel.description: Okay, so heres what happens. I run my server. People connect. It says something about Null disconnects. Also, It sometimes disconnects me and says "your account is already logged in" blahblah and it stays like that for about 30 seconds. And it says something about Invalid server. I cant post pictures because i'm on windows 5 and cant screenshot anything.
